    "### A2.1 Construction de la matrice document-terme\n",
    "\n",
    "GuidedLDA utilise l'interface scikit-learn (matrice sparse) au lieu de gensim.\n",
    "On reconstruit donc la matrice a partir des textes tokenisés."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 40,
   "id": "8909bcdc",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "ename": "NameError",
     "evalue": "name 'CountVectorizer' is not defined",
